# ============================================
# Streaming-US - United States Streaming Supplement
# ============================================
# Strategy Group: Streaming-US
# Purpose: Supplemental US streaming rules not covered by individual service files
# Coverage: Peacock, Paramount+, AMC+, Crunchyroll, Fubo, Sling, Philo,
#           Tubi, Pluto TV, Crackle, ESPN, BritBox, Shudder, Mubi, etc.
# Node Requirement: US node with unlock capability
# Note: Use alongside Disney Plus.list, Max.list, Hulu.list, Spotify.list, etc.
# ============================================

